    {
      "name": "Size Matters",
      "type": "ability",
      "system": {
        "description": "<p>The size of this demon determines its stats. The numbers listed are for its minimum size: Small. For each size above that, all its stats and damage increase by 2 and Wound severity increases by 1. Fear does not change.</p>",
