    },
    {
      "name": "Envelope",
      "type": "ability",
      "system": {
        "description": "<p>The demon makes an attack against a target, attempting to wrap itself around its prey. If successful, instead of dealing damage the target is Restrained and will begin to suffocate soon. The target can attempt a TN 6 Exertion roll to break free on his turn. The demon can envelope a single target of one size greater than itself, two of equal size, four of one size less, or eight of two sizes less. In cases where the demon has enveloped several targets of various sizes, two Tiny targets count as one Small, two Small count as one Medium, two Medium as one Large, two Large as one Huge, and two Huge count as one Massive.</p>",
        "action": "major"
      },
